    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Bothrops (Serpentes: Viperidae: Crotalinae) from Pampas del Heath, southeastern Peru, with comments on the systematics of the Bothrops neuwiedi species group" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590238>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590240>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590242>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590234> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590238>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Bothrops sonene sp. nov. (MUSA 4350) from Pampas del Heath, Bahuaja-Sonene National Park, department of Madre de Dios, Peru." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2590238/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590240>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Dorsal view of the holotype (MUBI 12319—A, 1073 mm TL) and paratypes (MUBI 14679—B, 553 mm TL, MUSA 4350—C, 435 mm TL, MUSM 33453—D, 339 mm TL) of Bothrops sonene. Ventral view of holotype (MUBI 12319— E) and paratype (MUBI 14679—F). TL= total length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2590240/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590242>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Dorsolateral view of head of the paratype (MUSA 4350—A, D, 20 mm HL) and holotype (MUBI 12319—B, 44.8 mm HL), and dorsal view of head (MUBI 14679—C, 23 mm HL) of the paratype of Bothrops sonene. HL= head length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2590242/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2590234>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Distribution of the lineages of the Bothrops neuwiedi species group. Symbols are as follow: stars = type localities, circles = records of specimens with DNA samples, squares = records of specimens that were only examined morphologically." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2590234/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

